                "name": "Personal Fitness", "avg_duration": "50-60", "sales_pitch": "A healthy body is essential for a healthy mind, and our Focus on Personal Fitness brings you a tailor made programme of courses that focus on your physical wellbeing, ensuring you are ready to take advantage of all life\u2019s opportunities. You\u2019ll learn how to avoid injury, optimise your training and develop your personal performances. This Learning Path will help you improve your core strength, flexibility and stamina with a variety of workout routines including strength-training, calisthenics, plyometrics and yoga.", "description": "Personal fitness is hugely important for your health and wellbeing. Keeping fit and healthy improves your quality of life in many areas. \r\n\r\nBy studying the Alison Learning Path in Personal Fitness you will learn ways in which to improve your personal health and fitness. You will learn fitness tips to help you exercise in the best way possible. You will learn yoga exercises to improve your core strength and flexibility. You will also learn how to exercise safely and avoid injuries.\r\n\r\nThe Alison Learning Path in Personal Fitness is a series of courses that cover ways in which to work on your personal fitness and wellbeing in order to live the healthiest life possible.", "learning_paths_type": "broaden", "courses": ["Personal Health and Fitness", "Physical Fitness - Fitness Tips and Workout Routines", "Health and Fitness - Running Tips, Swimming and Strength Training", "Yoga Exercises", "Yoga Exercises for Core Strength and Flexibility", "Physical Fitness - How to Avoid Injuries and Train Safely"]
